(1, 'Brighton Bed', 'bed1.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nSleek and sheltering, Pavillion makes a sophisticated sleep statement in solid mahogany and mahogany veneer with a black lacquer finish. Dramatically tapered posts support canopy rails that lend themselves to romantic draping. Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required. Mattresses and optional bunky board available (sold separately).\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Solid mahogany, mahogany veneer and low-emission engineered wood                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Black lacquer finish                                         </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Slat system with support legs                                     </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required                                     </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Maximum weight 800 pounds (includes weight of mattress, optional foundation, occupants)                             </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Fully disassembles for ease of delivery and installation                                              </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in Indonesia                                              </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 67&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 49&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 75&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n       \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> \r\n', 'bed', 11570, 'bigBed1.jpg:bigBed1and1.jpg:bigBed1and2.jpg:bigBed1and3.jpg'),
(2, 'Atwood Bed', 'bed2.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\n Contemporary platform bed is a minimalist marriage of cool, raw steel and warm, natural bamboo. Solid bamboo finished in warm smoke cuts a lean profile, squaring off in a striking partitioned headboard of rolled steel. Triangular tubular steel feet complete the modern, eclectic look. Each bed is expertly crafted using no nails or screws. Platform bed is designed for use with mattress; no foundation required. Mattresses and optional bunky board available, sold separately.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Created in collaboration with designer Maria Yee                      </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Solid bamboo                                         </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Cold-rolled steel headboard                                    </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Steel slat system with support legs                                    </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Tubular steel feet                            </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Joinery uses no nails or screws                                             </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required                                              </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Maximum weight capacity: 800 pounds (includes weight of mattress, optional foundation, occupants)                                           </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in China                                            </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 70&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 49&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 85&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n       \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'bed', 9920, 'bigBed2.jpg:bigBed2and1.jpg:bigBed2and2.jpg'),
(3, 'Asher Bed', 'bed3.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nOur new mid-century-inspired bedroom takes a distinctive step into a modern new century. Its bold presence and depth are achieved with mitered beveled frames that recess into panels handsomely crafted in solid shesham and mango wood. Enhanced with a tinted matte carnuba wax enriched with silky coats of lacquer to reveal the woodgrain\'s natural range of highlights. Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required. Mattresses and optional bunky board available (sold separately).\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Solid shesham and mango wood                      </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Tinted matte wax and lacquer finish                                         </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Slat system with support leg                                    </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required                                   </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Maximum weight 800 pounds (includes weight of mattress, optional foundation, occupants)                             </p></li>\r\n\r\n            <li><p>             Made in India                                             </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 54&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 30&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 83&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n       \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'bed', 13230, 'bigBed3.jpg:bigBed3and1.jpg:bigBed3and2.jpg'),
(4, 'Dawson Bed', 'bed4.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nWe\'ve modernized classic cottage styling without sacrificing an ounce of charm. Linear head and footboard are crafted with traditional board and batten detailing and dressed in a rich coffee finish. Even the posts and finials are squared off for a fresh, clean look. Versatile bed has two setting options for the side rails: Low accommodates a mattress and foundation; high accommodates a mattress only, leaving room under the bed for storage. Trundle available for twin size bed only. Mattresses and foundations also available (sold separately).\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Solid poplar, birch and hardwood veneer, and engineered wood                      </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Coffee finish with protective lacquer                                        </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Adjustable for mattress and foundation or mattress only for under-bed storage                                    </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Slat system with support legs                                    </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Trundle bed accommodates our 38\"x70\" trundle mattress                             </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Fully disassembles for ease of delivery and installation                                              </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in Vietnam                                             </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 44.5&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 81&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 54.5&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n       \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'bed', 9090, 'bigBed4.jpg:bigBed4and1.jpg:bigBed4and2.jpg:bigBed4and3.jpg'),
(5, 'LaSalla Bed', 'bed5.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nSleek contours and retro curves recall the streamlined simplicity of Art Moderne. Crafted in solid maple, solid ash and engineered wood, the curvilinear frame\'s clean horizontal banding, smooth radial corners and tapered legs are showcased by a rich catalyzed black satin lacquer finish. Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required. Mattresses and optional bunky board available (sold separately).\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Solid maple, solid ash and engineered wood                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Catalyzed black satin lacquer                                         </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Slat system with support leg                                    </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required                                   </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Maximum weight 800 pounds (includes weight of mattress, optional foundation, occupants)                             </p></li>\r\n\r\n            <li><p>             Made in USA                                              </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 56&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 42&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 75&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n       \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'bed', 11570, 'bigBed5.jpg:bigBed5and1.jpg:bigBed5and2.jpg'),
(6, 'Varick Bed', 'bed6.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nWe\'ve given the classic platform bed a glamorous makeover in soft alabaster linen and brushed pewter nailhead trim. All-natural linen covers the plush camelback headboard, as well as the foot and side rails. Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required. Mattresses and optional bunky board available (sold separately).\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Certified sustainable kiln-dried hardwood frame                      </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Soy-based foam cushioning                                        </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Fully upholstered headboard, foot and side rails                                    </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Flared wood legs have a dark tuxedo finish                                    </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Slat system with support legs                            </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required                                             </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in Libya                                              </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 39&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 35&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 84&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n       \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'bed', 12400, 'bigBed6.jpg:bigBed6and1.jpg:bigBed6and2.jpg'),
(7, 'Dash Bed', 'bed7.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nSophisticated framing in a translucent, matte espresso/grey finish is punctuated by graphic headboard cutouts and beveled detailing. Head- and footboard panels upholstered in a textured neutral add contrast. Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required. Mattresses and optional bunky board available (sold separately).\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Solid alder and alder veneers, with low-emission engineered wood                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Translucent espresso/grey matte lacquer finish                                        </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Polyester-rayon blend fabric panels                                   </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required                                     </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Maximum weight 800 pounds (includes weight of mattress, optional foundation, occupants)                             </p></li>\r\n\r\n            <li><p>             Made in Finland                                             </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 45&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 20&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 78.8&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n       \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'bed', 14880, 'bigBed7.jpg:bigBed7and1.jpg'),
(8, 'Cubix Bed', 'bed8.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nSustainable solid mango wood, with characteristic open grain and knots, and a rich clove stain set the tone for this clean-lined, beautifully detailed collection. Comfortably curved headboard is solid mango wood, mango veneer and low-emission engineered wood. Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required. Mattresses and optional bunky board available (sold separately).\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>        Solid sustainable mango wood, mango veneer and low-emission engineered wood                            </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>        Clove stain with lacquer finish                            </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>        Slat system with support legs                            </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>        Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required                            </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>         Maximum weight capacity: 800 pounds (includes weight of mattress, optional foundation, occupants)                           </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>          Made in Sweden                          </p></li>\r\n            \r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 55&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 32&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 79.5&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n       \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'bed', 10740, 'bigBed8.jpg:bigBed8and1.jpg:bigBed8and2.jpg'),
(9, 'Steppe Bed', 'bed9.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nA mid-century modernist\'s dream. Streamlined, low platform design is wrapped head to toe in a textural gold-hued khaki, treated with fabric protection and punctuated with retro button tufting on the headboard. Dark tapered legs take a minimal stance. Also stocked in charcoal fabric or chocolate leather. Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required. Mattresses and optional bunky board available (sold separately).\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>        Certified sustainable kiln-dried hardwood frame                            </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>        Soy-based foam cushioning                            </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>         Poly-cotton-acrylic blend fabric                           </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>         Fabric has soil and stain protectant                           </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>         Slat system with support legs                           </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>         Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required                           </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>          Made in Russia                          </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 40&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 30&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 70&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n       \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'bed', 7430, 'bigBed9.jpg:bigBed9and1.jpg'),
(10, 'Tate Bed', 'bed10.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nThe classic four-poster gets a modern Italian update in soothing taupe with whitewash. Hand-distressed finish lends artisanal detail and character to the clean-framed headboard, low platform and elegantly tapered posts with angled legs. Platform bed is designed for use with mattress; no foundation required. Mattresses and optional bunky board available, sold separately.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>           Poplar veneer and engineered wood                         </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>            Solid poplar posts                        </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Hand-distressed                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Taupe with whitewash finish                      </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Fir and poplar wood slat system with support legs                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in Italy                       </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 35&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 40&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 85&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n       \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'bed', 13230, 'bigBed10.jpg:bigBed10and1.jpg'),
(11, 'Harbor Bed', 'bed11.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nA mid-century modernist\'s dream. Streamlined, low platform design is wrapped head to toe in a textural charcoal weave, treated with fabric protection and punctuated with retro button tufting on the headboard. Dark tapered legs take a minimal stance. Also stocked in khaki fabric or chocolate leather. Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required. Mattresses and optional bunky board available (sold separately).\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>      Certified sustainable kiln-dried hardwood frame                              </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>      Soy-based foam cushioning                              </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>      Poly-cotton-acrylic blend fabric                              </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>      Fabric has soil and stain protectant                              </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>      Slat system with support legs                              </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>      Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required                              </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>       Made in Mongolia                             </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 36&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 25&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 89&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n       \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'bed', 19230, 'bigBed11.jpg:bigBed11and1.jpg:bigBed11and2.jpg:bigBed11and3.jpg'),
(12, 'Sierra Bed', 'bed12.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nClean lines align in an open airy bed that marries earthy fiber and natural wood. Slightly angled headboard is wrapped in a textural weave of 100% jute webbing that complements the linear design and organic beauty of the solid oak and oak veneer frame. Clear finish accentuates the wood\'s knots, grain, texture and color. Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required. Mattresses and optional bunky board available, sold separately.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>        Solid oak and oak veneer frame with water-based finish                            </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>        100% jute strapping                             </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>         Solid pine slat system with support legs                          </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>         Platform bed designed for use with mattress; no foundation required                           </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>         Maximum weight capacity: 800 pounds (includes weight of mattress, optional foundation, occupants)                           </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>                                    </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>          Made in Iran                          </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 40&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 29&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 79.80&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n       \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'bed', 12400, 'bigBed12.jpg:bigBed12and1.jpg:bigBed12and2.jpg:bigBed12and3.jpg'),
(13, 'Eiffel Chair', 'chair1.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\n            The elegant lines of the classic library wingback \r\n            unwind unexpectedly into a streamlined recliner. \r\n            Even the hidden pushback mechanism conceals its \r\n            relaxed side. Impeccably tailored in top-grain, \r\n            full-aniline-dyed leather in luscious cherry with \r\n            subtle black undertones that lend a multidimensional \r\n            effect. Self-welt detail traces sleek frame from \r\n            curved profile to keyhole arms. And the comfort \r\n            level is anything but stuffy. Sink-in soft \r\n            fiber-down blend cushion invites long reads \r\n            and longer conversations.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n                \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>Eco-friendly construction</p></li>\r\n            <li><p>Certified sustainable, kiln-dried solid maple and oak hardwood frame</p></li>\r\n            <li><p>Tight seat and back with soy-based polyfoam and fiber cushioning</p></li>\r\n            <li><p>Sinuous wire spring suspension</p></li>\r\n            <li><p>Hardwood legs with a Deco finish</p></li>\r\n            <li><p>100% polyester upholstery</p></li>\r\n            <li><p>Self-welt detailing</p></li>\r\n            <li><p>Benchmade</p></li>\r\n            <li><p>Made in Virginia, USA</p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>Width: 30.5&quot; </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>Depth: 28&quot;</p></li> \r\n            <li><p>Height: 30.5&quot;</p></li> \r\n            <li><p>SeatDepth: 22&quot;</p></li> \r\n            <li><p>Height: 19.25&quot;</p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>        \r\n   ', 'chair', 8260, 'bigChair1.j