(15, 'Klyne Slipcovered Chair', 'chair3.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\n            Our Klyne Chair and a Half is a compact lounge whose warm grey lines refresh the room with a casual attitude. Bigger than a chair, smaller than a loveseat and perfect for apartments and smaller home or use in conversational pairs for larger spaces. Narrow tapered arms cut a sleek profile and make for an even roomier experience. For the ultimate lounge, pull up the optional matching Klyne Ottoman and a Half.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n           \r\n            <li><p>             Certified sustainable kiln-dried hardwood frame                         </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Seat cushions are soy- or plant-based polyfoam encased in synthetic ticking          </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Tight back is filled with soy-based polyfoam and       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Eight-way, hand-tied spring suspension with partially  </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Back cushions are fiber in synthetic ticking                        </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Flexolator spring suspension                                    </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Benchmade                                              </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Upholstered in polyester                            </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 48&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 40&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 27&quot;                </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             SeatDepth: 23&quot;       