(16, 'Taraval Chair', 'chair4.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\n            Quintessential European design pays homage to the original modular sectional with an emphasis on classic low lines and unparalleled comfort. Chunky basketweave in heathered neutrals plays up Moda\'s interesting proportions, from slim lower rails and boxy, deep cushions to a smart angled back.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Seat cushion is innerspring coil unit surrounded by        </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Certified sustainable kiln-dried hardwood frame                         </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Seat cushions are soy- or plant-based polyfoam encased in synthetic ticking          </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Tight back is filled with soy-based polyfoam and                </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Eight-way, hand-tied spring suspension with partially           </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Back cushions are fiber in synthetic ticking                        </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Benchmade                                                   </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Sinuous wire suspension                                             </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in Virginia, USA                                     </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 34&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 38&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 28.5&quot;                </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             SeatDepth: 32&quot;          