(18, 'Blake Lounge Chair', 'chair6.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\n            An unexpected mix of materials espresso solid teak, handwoven natural rattan and chocolate top-grain, full-aniline leather with a handsome aged patina adds a great primitive/modern accent to the room. Handcrafted with attention to detail, there\'s even a strong webbed suspension under the woven rattan seat, and the cushions are plumped with polyfiber wrapped in ticking. A great chair in pairs.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Solid teak        </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Sustainable, woven mesh                      </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Top-grain, full-aniline leather          </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Frame has an espresso finish               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Eight-way, hand-tied spring suspension with partially           </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Back cushions are fiber in synthetic ticking                        </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in Indonesia and USA                                    </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 30&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 30&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 34&quot;                </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             SeatDepth: 21.5&quot;             </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 5&quot;             </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'chair', 9920, 'bigChair6.jpg:bigChair6and1.jpg:bigChair6and2.jpg:bigChair6and3.jpg'),
(19, 'Ankara Chair', 'chair7.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\n            An eye-catching chair designed to be seen from every angle. Gracefully curved barrel back is precision-cut of mahogany veneer over engineered wood in an intricate pattern inspired by Indonesian mosaics. Solid mahogany frame flows seamlessly from the clean, contemporary sweep of the arms to the tapered back legs that follow the downward angle of the upper framework\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Plantation grown solid mahogany and mahogany veneer over engineered wood        </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Warm java finish and clear protective lacquer                        </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Seat cushion is soy-based polyfoam with fiber          </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Stain-resistant cushion cover is woven polyester          </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Back cushions are fiber in synthetic ticking                        </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Cushion is polyfoam with fiber in downproof ticking                                                 </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Cane seat with synthetic web suspension                                            </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in USA and Indonesia                                    </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 29&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 28&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 30&quot;                </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             SeatDepth: 26&quot;         