(25, 'Brown Chair', 'chair13.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nOur reinterpretation of the leather wingback is a refined new classic, no tufts or fuss. Sheltering wings curve clean to narrow arms and straight lines at the base, all outlined in antiqued brass nailheads, each applied by hand the old-fashioned way. The heritage of fine leather continues; this top-grain leather, full-aniline dyed a dark java, marbled with high and low tones with a wax finish, will develop a rich patina over time. Hardwood legs taper square in distressed mahogany.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Eco-friendly construction                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Certified sustainable kiln-dried hardwood frame                                           </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Seat cushion is soy-based polyfoam with fiber wrapped in feather-down blend                                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Tight back is soy-based polyfoam                                    </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Full-aniline leather                                </p></li>\r\n <li><p>             Nailhead trim                              </p></li>\r\n <li><p>             Made in France                                </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 35&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 40.5&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 42.5&quot;                </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             SeatDepth: 21.25&quot;             </p></li> \r\n          \r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'chair', 15000, 'bigChair13.jpg:bigChair13and1.jpg:bigChair13and2.jpg:bigChair13and3.jpg'),
(26, 'Avery Bomb Chest', 'chest1.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nWe\'ve romanced a classic bombe shape with a cleaner, contemporary aesthetic. Sensuous curves from every angle are enhanced with warm caramel undertones in the slightly distressed charcoal finish. Three generous drawers are lined with hand-silkscreened paper in a black-on-cream vine pattern and finished with brushed nickel pulls.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Solid poplar, red birch and engineered wood                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Medium-gloss black finish with clear protective lacquer                                         </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Dovetail joinery on drawers                                    </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Brushed nickel hardware                                   </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in China                                </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 35&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 20.5&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 23.5&quot;                </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             WoodDepth: 8.25&quot;             </p></li> \r\n            \r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'chest', 743, 'bigChest1.jpg:bigChest1and1.jpg:bigChest1and2.jpg:bigChest1and3.jpg'),
(27, 'Kavari Chest', 'chest2.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nOur sleek new \"antique\" of richly grained acacia wood meets the modern demand for compact storage with open and closed spaces. Each piece is handcrafted with tongue-and-groove joinery and hand-finished with a two-tone distressing technique that produces a rich, glowing brown patina with undertones of black. \r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Acacia wood                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Multistep hand-finish                                            </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Iron hinges, handle and knobs with antiqued bronze finish                                      </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Three drawers                                  </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Cord management cutouts                                </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in India                                </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 40&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 20&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 28&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n            <h5>Door Overall:</h5>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 21&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 17&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 21&quot;                </p></li>\r\n       </ul> \r\n           <h5>Shelf Overall:</h5>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 21&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 17&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 0.5&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'chest', 495, 'bigChest2.jpg:bigChest2and1.jpg:bigChest2and2.jpg:bigChest2and3.jpg'),
(28, 'Rojo Chest', 'chest3.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nWith all the warmth and rustic charm of a one-of-a-kind antique, the rich waxed patina of this red storage cabinet adds instant character to any room. Crafted of shesham and mango wood with traditional tongue-and-groove joinery, the cabinet is topped with architectural crown moulding.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Sustainable shesham and mango wood                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Red lacquer finish with pigmented wax                                           </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Iron hinges and knobs                                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Two adjustable shelves                                     </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Cord management with sliding door                               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in India                                              </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 46&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 18&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 34&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n      <h5>Door Overall:</h5>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 18&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 15&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 25&quot;                </p></li>\r\n        </ul> \r\n           <h5>Shelf Overall:</h5>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 20&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 14&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 0.5&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'chest', 661, 'bigChest3.jpg:bigChest3and1.jpg:bigChest3and2.jpg:bigChest3and3.jpg'),
(29, 'Kavar 40 Chest', 'chest4.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nOur sleek new \"antique\" of richly grained acacia wood warms the entryway with the look of a well-loved family heirloom. Classic cabinet has one fixed shelf and two storage drawers. Each piece is constructed with mortise-and-tenon joinery and hand-finished with a two-tone distressing technique that produces a rich, glowing brown patina with undertones of black. Clean crown moulding, raised panel doors and hand-finished iron hardware add character.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Acacia wood                      </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Edge-to-edge planks and tongue-and-groove frame joinery                                          </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Iron hardware                                      </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Lacquer finish                                  </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Two drawers with wood channel glides and stoppers                              </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             One fixed shelf                                            </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in Venezuela                                           </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 40&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 15&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 36&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n      <h5>Door Overall:</h5>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 18&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 12&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 23&quot;                </p></li>\r\n        </ul> \r\n           <h5>Shelf Overall:</h5>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 18&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 12&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 10&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div> \r\n', 'chest', 495, 'bigChest4.jpg:bigChest4and1.jpg:bigChest4and2.jpg:bigChest4and3.jpg'),
(30, 'Dawson Chest', 'chest5.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nOur architectural Paterson collection is inspired by built-in cabinetry from turn-of-the-century homes. Contemporary cabinet with a touch of cottage styling features stepped moulding, elegant tapered legs, a white lacquer finish and brushed nickel handles. Arts-and-Crafts style windowpane doors open to two adjustable shelves.\r\n\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Solid hardwood and low-emission engineered wood                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             White lacquer finish                                          </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Brushed nickel hardware                                      </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Tempered glass door panes                                     </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Two adjustable shelves                              </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in Thailand                                              </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 36&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 15&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 49&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n      <h5>Door Overall:</h5>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 33&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 14&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 22&quot;                </p></li>\r\n        </ul> \r\n           <h5>Shelf Overall:</h5>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 32&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 12&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 42&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div> \r\n', 'chest', 495, 'bigChest5.jpg:bigChest5and1.jpg:bigChest5and2.jpg:bigChest5and3.jpg'),
(31, 'Parker Spirit Chest', 'chest6.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nThere\'s more than meets the eye in our new compact entertainment bar. Two bartop leaves flip open to perch drinks and snacks, while revealing generous bottle storage. Front door drops down to create an open serving area. Below are a drawer for tools and an 18-bottle wine bin. Side shelves (three on the left, two on the right) store stemware or bottles. Finished back panel lets Parker be the center of the party.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Solid birch, solid ash and ash veneer, low-emission engineered wood                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Black lacquer finish                                          </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Brushed nickel-finish pulls                                      </p></li>\r\n        \r\n            <li><p>             Made in Columbia                                              </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 33&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 16&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 36&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n      <h5>Door Overall:</h5>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 44&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 16&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 37&quot;                </p></li>\r\n        </ul> \r\n           <h5>Shelf Overall:</h5>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 21&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 9&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 25&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'chest', 661, 'bigChest6.jpg:bigChest6and1.jpg:bigChest6and2.jpg:bigChest6and3.jpg'),
(32, 'Ainsworth Chest', 'chest7.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nTimeless styling and a versatile collection of pieces with glass and wood panel options offer media, storage and workspace solutions for every setting. American-crafted cabinetry showcases a return to walnut with its lighter mid-tone hue and minimal figured grain. Natural oil and wax finish highlights and nourishes the wood.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Solid American walnut, walnut veneer and low-emission engineered wood                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Natural oil and wax finish                                          </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Zinc hardware with a natural steel finish                                      </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Includes both wood and glass door panels                                    </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Three adjustable shelves                              </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in USA                                            </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 40&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 17&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 60&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n      <h5>Door Overall:</h5>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 34&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 16&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 48&quot;                </p></li>\r\n        </ul> \r\n           <h5>Shelf Overall:</h5>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 35&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 42&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 32.5&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'chest', 1323, 'bigChest7.jpg:bigChest7and1.jpg:bigChest7and2.jpg'),
(33, 'Varick Chest', 'chest8.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nElongated solid brass pulls make a symmetrical play of storage in tall slender cabinet that leaves a small footprint with maximum presence. Revealing glass-paneled oak-veneered doors open to three shelves with a plate rail on the top shelf. A generous drawer below stows linens, trays or odds and ends.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Double oak veneer and low-emission engineered wood                      </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Durable lacquer coffee finish                                           </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             One fixed and two adjustable shelves                                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Solid brass handles                                    </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Anti-tip hardware included                               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in Chile                                              </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 40&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 16.5&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 76&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n  \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'chest', 743, 'bigChest8.jpg:bigChest8and1.jpg:bigChest8and2.jpg:bigChest8and3.jpg'),
(34, 'Hunter Chest', 'chest9.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nInspired by a vintage steamer trunk, our updated steamer bar cabinet opens to reveal a capacious home bar. Crafted of American ash solids and veneers with a distinctive recessed panel grid design, rich ebony finish and satin silver finished hardware. Storage includes two fixed shelves, bottle storage on both doors, laminate fold-out top, pull-out glass racks for up to 30 wine glasses and 20 drinking glasses, and an accessory drawer.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             American ash solids and veneers                     </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Hand-stained with an oil topcoat                                           </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Doweled joinery with dovetailed drawer boxes                                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Nickel-plated solid brass hardware                                   </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Two fixed shelves                              </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in Philippines                                              </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 37&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 21&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 42&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n      <h5>When Fully Opened:</h5>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 72&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 21.5&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 42&quot;                </p></li>\r\n        </ul> \r\n           \r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'chest', 854, 'bigChest9.jpg:bigChest9and1.jpg:bigChest9and2.jpg:bigChest9and3.jpg'),
(35, 'Marin Chest', 'chest10.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nCenturies of Chinese craftmanship meet mid-century modern in a warm, minimal classic. Crafted of solid weathered elm with traditional wood-on-wood joinery techniques without the use of nails or screws this contemporary cabinet combines generous storage with striking clean lines. A multi-step tung tree oil finish, a natural oil derived from the seeds of the tung tree nut, brings out the sweeping grain and preserves the beauty of the wood. Each door with solid steel pulls features built-in storage for bottles and barware.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Created in collaboration with designer Maria Yee                     </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Solid elm                                           </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Traditional wood-on-wood joinery                                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Tung tree oil exterior finish, water-based interior finish                                   </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Five shelves (one fixed, one adjustable, three adjustable                               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in Mexico                                              </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 37&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 21.5&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 42&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n     \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'chest', 495, 'bigChest10.jpg:bigChest10and1.jpg:bigChest10and2.jpg:bigChest10and3.jpg'),
(36, 'Steamer Chest', 'chest11.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nOur refined yet rustic trunk table is crafted of solid shesham wood with a warm clove finish, beautiful beveled panels and traditional iron hardware. Top with safety hinges opens up to generous, deep storage with features including a removable serving tray and removable dividers for stashing up to eight bottles of wine.\r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Solid shesham wood                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Clove lacquer finish                                          </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Iron hardware with clear powdercoat finish                                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Two adjustable shelves                                     </p></li>\r\n            \r\n            <li><p>             Made in Canada                                            </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 44&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 24&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 18&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n      \r\n       \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'chest', 570, 'bigChest11.jpg:bigChest11and1.jpg:bigChest11and2.jpg:bigChest11and3.jpg'),
(37, 'Calasis Chest', 'chest12.jpg', '<div id=\'prodDescDiv\'>\r\n    <div id=\'descDiv1\'>\r\n        <h4>Overview</h4>\r\n        <p>\r\nTimeless styling and a versatile collection of pieces with glass and wood panel options offer media, storage and workspace solutions for every setting. American-crafted cabinetry showcases a return to walnut with its lighter mid-tone hue and minimal figured grain. Natural oil and wax finish highlights and nourishes the wood. Interchangeable door panels easily allow transition from open to closed storage. \r\n        </p>\r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>!!stop!!\r\n       \r\n        <hr class=\'thinLine\'/>\r\n        <h4>Details and Dimensions</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Solid American walnut, walnut veneer and low-emission engineered wood                      </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Natural oil and wax finish                                           </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Zinc hardware with a natural steel finish                                       </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Includes both wood and glass door panels                                    </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Three adjustable shelves                               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Cord management/ventilation cutout                                              </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Made in Vietnam                                              </p></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <hr/>\r\n        <h4>Overall Dimensions:</h4>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 40&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 17&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 60&quot;                </p></li> \r\n        </ul>\r\n      <h5>Overall interior:</h5>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><p>             Width: 34.75&quot;               </p></li>\r\n            <li><p>             Depth: 16&quot;                 </p></li> \r\n            <li><p>             Height: 48&quot;                </p></li>\r\n        </ul> \r\n        \r\n    </div>\r\n</div> ', 'chest', 755, 'bigChest12.jpg:bigChest12and1.jpg:bigChest12and2.jpg');

